item.title: CVE-2017-10933|2024-08-05T17:50:12.719Z -- zte -- zxdt22%20sf01
item.description: All versions prior to V2.06.00.00 of ZTE ZXDT22 SF01, an monitoring system of ZTE energy product, are impacted by directory traversal vulnerability that allows remote attackers to read arbitrary files on the system via a full path name after host address.
